quran[357]{c,v,t}:
  36,28,Iss kay baad hum ney uss qom per aasman say koi lashkar na utara aur na iss tarah hum utara kertay hain
  36,29,Woh to sirf aik zor ki cheekh thi kay yakayak woh sab kay sab bujh bujha gaye
  36,30,(aisay) bando per afsos! Kabhi bhi koi rasool unn kay pass nahi aaya jiss ki hansi unhon ney na uraee ho
  36,31,Kiya unhon ney nahi dekha kay inn kay pehlay boht si qomon ko hum ney gharat ker diya kay woh unn ki taraf lot ker nahi aayen gay
  36,32,Aur nahi hai koi jamaat magar yeh kay woh jama hoker humaray samney hazir ki jayegi
  36,33,Aur inn kay liye aik nishani (khusk) zamin hai jiss ko hum ney zindah ker diya aur iss say ghalla nikala jiss mein say woh kahatay hain
  36,34,Aur hum ney iss mein khajooron kay aur angooron kay baghaat peda kerdiye aur jin mein hum ney chashmay bhi jari ker diye hain
  36,35,Takay (log) uss kay phal khayen aur iss ki inn kay hathon ney nahi banaya. Phir kiyon shukar guzari nahi kertay
  36,36,Woh pak zaat hai jiss ney her cheez kay joray peda kiye khua woh zamin ki ugaee hui cheezen hon khua khud unkay nafoos hon khua woh (cheezen) hon jinhen yeh jantay bhi nahi
  36,37,Aur inn kay liye aik nishani raat hai jiss say hum din ko kheench latay detay hain to yakayak andheray mein reh jatay hain
  36,38,Aur sooraj kay liye jo muqarrara raah hai woh ussi per chalta hai yeh hai muqarrar kerdah ghalib ba-ilm Allah Taalaa ka
  36,39,Aur chand ki hum ney manzilen muqarrar ker rahkhi hain yahan tak kay woh lot ker purani tehni ki tarah hojata hai
  36,40,Na aftab ki yeh majal hai kay chand ko pakray aur na raat din per aagay barh janey wali hai aur sab kay sab aasman mein tertay phirtay hain
  36,41,Aur inn kay liye aik nishani (yeh bhi) hai kay hum ney inn ki nasal ko bhari hui kashti mein sawar kiya
  36,42,Aur inn kay liye issi jaisi aur cheezen peda ken jin per yeh sawar hotay hain
  36,43,Aur agar hum chahatay to enhen dobo detay. Phir na to koi unn ka faryad rass hota na woh bachaye jayen
  36,44,Lekin hum apni taraf say rehmat kertay hain aur aik muddat tak kay liye unhen faeeday day rahey hain
  36,45,Aur inn say jab (kabhi) kaha jata hai kay aglay pichlay (gunahon) say bacho takay tum per reham kiya jaye
  36,46,Aur inn kay pass to inn kay rab ki nishaniyon mein say koi nishani aisi nahi aati jiss say yeh bey rukhi na barattay hon
  36,47,Aur inn say jab kaha jata hai kay Allah Taalaa kay diye huyey mein say kuch kharach kero to yeh kuffar eman walon ko jawab detay hain kay hum enhen kiyon khilayen? Jinhen agar Allah Taalaa chahata to khud khila pila deta tum to ho hi khulli gumrahi mein
  36,48,Woh kehtay hain kay yeh wada kab hoga sachay ho to batlao
  36,49,Enhen sirf aik sakht cheekh ka intezar hai jo enhen aa pakray gi aur yeh bahum laraee jhagray mein hi hongay
  36,50,Uss waqt na to yeh waseeyat ker saken gay aur na apnay ehal ki taraf lot saken gay
  36,51,To soor kay phoonkay jatay hi sab kay sab apni qabron say apnay perwerdigar ki taraf (tez tez) chalney lagen gay
  36,52,Kahen gay haye haye! Humen humari khuwab gahaon say kiss ney utha diya. Yehi hai jiss ka wada rehman ney diya tha aur rasoolon ney sach sach keh diya tha
  36,53,Yeh nahi hai magar aik cheekh kay yakayak saray kay saray humaray samney hazir ker diyey jayen gay
  36,54,Pus aaj kissi shaks per kuch bhi zulm na kiya jayega aur tumhen nahi badla diya jayega magar sirf unhi kamon ka jo tum kiya kertay thay
  36,55,Jannati log aaj kay din apnay (dilchasp)mashghalon mein hashash bashash hain
  36,56,Woh aur unn ki biwiyan sayon mein masheriyon per takiya lagaye bethay hongay
  36,57,Inn kay liye jannat mein her qisam kay meway hongay aur bhi jo kuch woh talab keren
  36,58,Meharbaan perwerdigar ki taraf say unhen salam kaha jayega
  36,59,Aey gunehgaron! Aaj tum alag hojao
  36,60,Aey aulad-e-adam! Kiya mein ney tum say qol-o-qarar nahi liya tha kay tum shetan ki ibadat na kerna woh to tumhara khulla dushman hai
  36,61,Aur meri hi ibadat kerna. Seedhi raah yehi hai
  36,62,Shetan ney to tum mein say boht sari makhlooq ko behka diya. Kiya tum aqal nahi raktay
  36,63,Yehi woh dozakh hai jiss ka tumhen wada diya jata tha
  36,64,Apnay kufur ka badla paney kay liye aaj iss mein dakhil hojao
  36,65,Hum aaj kay din inkay mun per mohar laga den gay aur inn kay hath hum say batein keren gay aur inn kay paaon gawaheeyian den gay unn kamon ki jo woh kertay thay
  36,66,Agar hum chahtay to inn ki aankhen bey noor ker detay phir yeh rastay ki taraf dortay phirtay lekin enhen kaisay dikhaee deta
  36,67,Aur agar hum chahatay to inn ki jaga hi per inn ki soorten masakh ker detay phir na woh chal phir saktay aur na lot saktay
  36,68,Aur jissay hum boorsha kertay hain ussay pedaeeshi halat ki taraf phir ulat detay hain kiya phir bhi woh nahi samajhtay
  36,69,Na to hum ney iss payghumber ko shair sikhaye aur na yeh iss kay laeeq hai. Woh to sirf naseehat aur wazeh quran hai
  36,70,Takay woh her uss shaks ko aagah kerday jo zindah hai aur kafiron per hujjat sabit hojaye
  36,71,Kiya woh nahi dekhtay kay hum ney apnay hathon banaee hui cheezon mein say unn kay liye chopaye (bhi) peda ker diye jin kay yeh malik hogaye hain
  36,72,Aur inn mawesheeyon ko hum ney unn ka tabey farman bana diya hai jin mein say baaz to inn ki sawariyan hain aur baaz ka gosht khatay hain
  36,73,Enhen unn say aur bhi boht faeeday hain aur peenay ki cheezen. Kiya phit (bhi) yeh shukar ada nahi keren gay
  36,74,Aur woh Allah kay siwa doosron ko mabood banatay hain takay woh madad kiye jayen
  36,75,(halankay) unn mein inn ki madad ki taqat hi nahi (lekin) phir bhi (musrikeen) unn kay liye hazir baash lashkari hain
  36,76,Pus aap ko inn ki baat ghumnaak na keray hum inn ki possheedah aur ailaniya sari baaton ko (ba-khoobi) jantay hain
  36,77,Kiya insan ko itna bhi maloom nahi kay hum ney ussay nutfay say peda kiya hai? Phir yakayak woh sarreh jhagraloo bann betha
  36,78,Aur uss ney humaray liye misal biyan ki aur apni (asal) pedaeesh ko bhool gaya kehney laga inn gali sarhi haddiyon ko kon zindah ker sakta hai
  36,79,Aap jawab dijiye! Kay enhen woh zindah keray ga jiss ney enhen awwal martaba peda kiya hai jo sab tarah ki pedaeesh ka ba-khoobi jannay wala hai
  36,80,Wohi jiss ney tumharay liye sabz darakht say aag peda kerdi jiss say tum yakayak aag sulgatay ho
  36,81,Jiss ney aasman aur zamin ko peda kiya hai kiya woh inn jeson kay peda kerney per qadir nahi be-shak qadir hai. Aur wohi to peda kerney wala dana (beena) hai
  36,82,Woh jab kisi cheez ka iradah kerta hai ussay itna farma dena (kafi hai) kay ho ja woh ussi waqt hojati hai
  36,83,Pus pak hai woh Allah jiss hath mein her cheez ki badshaat hai aur jiss ki taraf tum sab lotaye jaogay
  37,1,Qasam hai saf bandhney walay (farishton ki)
  37,2,Phir poori tarah dantney walon ki
  37,3,Phir zikar-e-Allah ki tilawat kerney walon ki
  37,4,Yaqeenan tum sab ka mabood aik hi hai
  37,5,Aasmano aur zamin aur inn kay darmiyan ki tamam cheezon aur mashriqon ka rab wohi hai
  37,6,Hum ney aasman-e-duniya ko sitaron ki zeenat say aaraasta kiya
  37,7,Aur hifazat ki sirkash shetan say
  37,8,Aalam-e-bala kay farishton (ki baaton) ko sunnay kay liye woh kaan bhi nahi laga saktay bulkay her taraf say woh maaray jatay hain
  37,9,Bhaganey kay liye aur unn kay liye daeemi azab hai
  37,10,Magar jo koi aik aadh baat uchak lay bhagay to (foran hi) uss kay peechay dehakta hua shola lag jata hai
  37,11,Inn kafiron say poocho to kay aaya inn ka peda kerna ziyadah dushwaar hai ya (unn ka) jinhen hum ney (inn kay ilawa) peda kiya? Hum ney (insano) ko less daar mitti say peda kiya hai
  37,12,Bulkay tu tajjub ker raha hai aur yeh maskhara pan ker rahey hain
  37,13,Aur jab enhen naseehat ki jati hai yeh nahi mantay
  37,14,Aur jab kissi moajzzay ko dekhtay hain to mazaq uratay hain
  37,15,Aur kehtay hain kay yeh to bilkul khullam khulla jadoo hi hai
  37,16,Kiya jab hum mar jayen gay aur khak aur haddi hojayen gay phir kiya (sach much) hum uthaye jayen gay
  37,17,Kiya hum say pehlay kay humaray baap dada bhi
  37,18,Aap jawab dijiye! Kay haan haan aur tum zaleel (bhi) howo gay
  37,19,Woh to sirf aik zor ki jhirki hai kay yakayak yeh dekhney lagay gay
  37,20,Aur kahen gay kay haye humari kharabi yehi jaza (saza) ka din hai
  37,21,Yehi faislay ka din hai jissay tum jhutlatay rahey
  37,22,Zalimon ko aur unn kay humrahiyon ko aur (jin) jin ki woh Allah kay ilawa parastish kertay thay
  37,23,(inn sab ko) jama kerkay enhen dozakh ki raah dikha do
  37,24,Aur enhen theraklo (iss liye) kay inn say (zaroori) sawal kiyey janay walay hain
  37,25,Tumhen kiya hogaya hai kay (iss waqt) tum aik doosray ki madad nahi kertay
  37,26,Bulkay woh (sab kay sab) aaj farmanbardaar bann gaye
  37,27,Woh aik doosray ki taraf mutawajja hoker sawal-o-jawab kerney lagen gay
  37,28,Kahen gay kay tum to humaray pass humari dayen taraf say aatay thay
  37,29,Woh jawab den gay kay nahi bulkay tum hi eman daar na thay
  37,30,Aur kuch humara zor to tum per tha (hi) nahi. Bulkay tum (khud) sirkash log thay
  37,31,Abb to hum (sab) per humaray rab ki yeh baat sabit ho chuki kay hum (azab) chakhney walay hain
  37,32,Pus hum ney tumhen gumrah kiya hum to khud bhi gumrah hi thay
  37,33,So abb aaj kay din to (sab kay sab) azab mein shareek hain
  37,34,Hum gunehgaaro kay sath issi tarah kiya kertay hain
  37,35,Yeh woh (log) hain kay jab inn say kaha jata hai kay Allah kay siwa koi mabood nahi to yeh sirkashi kertay thay
  37,36,Aur kehtay thay kay kiya hum apnay maboodon ko aik deewaney shaeer ki baat per chor den
  37,37,(nahi nahi) bulkay (nabi) to haq (sacha deen) laye hain aur sab rasoolon ko sach jantay hain
  37,38,Yaqeenan tum dard-naak azab (ka maza) chakhney walay ho
  37,39,Tumhen ussi ka badla diya jayega jo tum kertay thay
  37,40,Magar Allah Taalaa kay khalis bargazeedah banday
  37,41,Unhin kay liye muqarrara rozi hai
  37,42,(her tarah kay) meway aur ba-izzat-o-ikraam hongay
  37,43,Nematon wali jannaton mein
  37,44,Takhton per aik doosray kay samney (bethay) hongay
  37,45,Jaari sharab kay jaam ka unn per dor chal raha hoga
  37,46,Jo saaf shaffaf peenay mein lazeez hogi
  37,47,Na uss say dard-e-sir ho aur na uss kay peenay say behken
  37,48,Aur unn kay pass neechi nazron bari bari aankhon wali (hooren) hongi
  37,49,Aisi jesay chupaye huyey anday
  37,50,(jannati) aik doosray ki taraf rukh kerkay poochen gay
  37,51,Unn mein say aik kehney wala kahe ga mera aik sathi tha
  37,52,Jo (mujh say) kaha kerta tha kay kiya tu (qayamat kay aaney ka) yaqeen kerney walon mein say hai
  37,53,Kiya jab kay hum mar ker mitti aur haddi hojayen gay kiya uss waqt hum jaza diyey janey walay hain
  37,54,Kahey ga tum chahtay ho kay jhaank ker dekh lo
  37,55,Jhaanktay hi ussay beechon beech jahannum mein (jalta hua) dekhay ga
  37,56,Kahey ga Wallah! Qareeb tha kay tu mujhay (bhi) barbaad ker day
  37,57,Agar meray rab ka ehsan na hota to mein bhi dizakh mein hazir kiyey janey walon mein hota
  37,58,Kiya (yeh sahih hai) kay hum marney walay hi nahi
  37,59,Ba-juz pehli aik mot kay aur na hum azab kiyey janey walay hain
  37,60,Phir to (zahir baat hai kay) yeh bari kaamyabi hai
  37,61,Aisi (kaamyabi) kay liye amal kernay walon ko amal kerna chahayey
  37,62,Kiya yeh mehmaani achi hai ya seendh (zaqoom) ka darakht
  37,63,Jissay hum ney zalimon kay liye sakht aazmaeesh bana rakha hai
  37,64,Be-shak woh darakht jahannum ki jarr mein say nikalta hai
  37,65,Jiss kay khoshay shetan kay siron jesay hotay hain
  37,66,(jahannumi) issi darakht mein say khayen gay aur issi say pet bharen gay
  37,67,Phir iss per garum jaltay jaltay paani ki malooni hogi
  37,68,Phir inn sab ka lotna jahannum ki (aag kay dher ki) taraf hoga
  37,69,Yaqeen mano! Kay enhon ney apnay baap dadon ko behka hua paya
  37,70,Aur yeh unhi kay naqsh-e-qadam per dortay rahey
  37,71,Inn say pehlay bhi boht say aglay behak chukay hain
  37,72,Jinn mein hum ney daraney walay (rasool) bhejay thay
  37,73,Abb tu dekh ley jinhen dhamkaya gaya tha unn ka anjam kaisa kuch hua
  37,74,Siwaye Allah kay bargazeedah bandon kay
  37,75,Aur humen nooh (alh-e-salam) ney pukara to (dekhlo) hum kaisay achay dua qabool kerney walay hain
  37,76,Hum ney ussay aur uss kay ghar walon ko uss zabardast museebat say bacha liya
  37,77,Aur uss ki aulad ko hum ney baqi rehney wali bana di
  37,78,Aur hum ney uss ka (zikar-e-khair) pichlon mein baqi rakha
  37,79,Nooh (alh-e-salam) per tamam jahano mein salam ho
  37,80,Hum neki kerney walon ko issi tarah badlay detay hain
  37,81,Woh humaray eman daar bandon mein say tha
  37,82,Phir hum ney doosron ko dobo diya
  37,83,Aur uss (nooh alh-e-salam ki) tabeydaari kerney walon mein say (hi) ibrahim (alh-e-salam bhi) thay
  37,84,Jabkay apany rab kay pass bey-aib dil laye
  37,85,Unhon ney apnay baap aur apni qom say kaha kay tum kiya pooj rahey ho
  37,86,Kiya tum Allah kay siwa gharay huyey maboob chahtay ho
  37,87,To yeh (batlao kay) tum ney rab-ul-aalameen ko kiya samjh rakha hai
  37,88,Abb ibrahim (alh-e-salam) ney aik nigah sitaron ki taraf uthaee
  37,89,Aur kaha mein to beemar hun
  37,90,Iss per woh sab uss say mun moray huyey wapis chalay gaye
  37,91,Aap (chup chupatay) unn kay maboodon kay pass gaye aur farmaney lagay tum khatay kiyon nahi
  37,92,Tumhen kiya hogaya kay baat tak nahi kertay
  37,93,Phir to (poori qooat kay sath) dayen hath say unhen maarney per pal paray
  37,94,Woh (butt parast) doray bhagay aap ki taraf mutawajja huyey
  37,95,To aap ney farmaya tum enhen poojtay ho jinhen (khud) tum tarashtay ho
  37,96,Halankay tumhen aur tumhari banaee hui cheezon ko Allah hi ney peda kiya hai
  37,97,Woh kehney lagay iss kay liye aik makan banao aur iss (dekakti hui) aag mein issay daal do
  37,98,Unhon ney to iss (ibrahim alh-e-salam) kay sath makar kerna chaha lekin hum ney unhi ko neecha ker diya
  37,99,Aur uss (ibrahim alh-e-salam) ney kaha mein to hijrat kerkay apnay perwerdigar ki taraf janey wala hun. Woh zaroor meri rehnumaee keray ga
  37,100,Aey meray rab! Mujhay nek bakht aulad ata farma
  37,101,To hum ney ussay aik burd-baar bachay ki bisharat di
  37,102,Phir jab woh (bacha) itni umar ko phoncha kay uss kay sath chalay phiray to uss (ibrahim alh-e-salam) ney kaha meray piyaray bachay! Mein khuwab mein apnay aap ko tujhay zibah kertay huyey dekh raha hun. Abb tu bata kay teri kiya raye hai? Betay ney jawab diya kay abba! Jo hukum hua hai ussay baja layiye inshaAllah aap mujhay sabar kerney walon mein say payen gay
  37,103,Gharz jab dono mutee hogaye aur uss ney (baap ney) uss ko (betay ko) paishaani kay bal gira diya
  37,104,To hum ney aawaz di kay aey ibrahim
  37,105,Yaqeenan tu ney apna khuwab sacha ker dikhaya be-shak hum neki kerney walon ko issi tarah jaza detay hain
  37,106,Dar-haqeeqat yeh khulla imtehan tha
  37,107,Aur hum ney aik bara zabeeha iss kay fidyey mein dey diya
  37,108,Aur hum ney unn ka zikar-e-khair pichlon mein baqi rakha
  37,109,Ibrahim (alh-e-salam) per salam ho
  37,110,Hum neko karon ko issi tarah badla detay hain
  37,111,Be-shak woh humaray eman daar bandon mein say tha
  37,112,Aur hum ney uss ko ishaq (alh-e-salam) nabi ki bisharat di jo saleh logon mein say hoga
  37,113,Aur hum ney ibrahim-o-ishaq (al-e-heem-us-salam) per barkaten nazil farmaeen aur inn dono ki aulad mein baazay to nek bakht hain aur baaz apnay nafs per sareeh zulm kerney walay hain
  37,114,Yaqeenan hum ney musa aur haroon (al-e-heem-us-salam) per bara ehsan kiya
  37,115,Aur unhen aur unn ki qom ko baray dukh dard say nijat dey di
  37,116,Aur unn ki madad ki to wohi ghalib rahey
  37,117,Aur hum ney unhen (wazeh aur) roshan kitab di
  37,118,Aur unhen seedhay rastay per qaeem rakha
  37,119,Aur hum ney unn dono kay liye peechay aanay walon mein yeh baat baqi rakhi
  37,120,Kay musa aur haroon (al-e-heem-us-salam) per salam ho
  37,121,Be-shak hum nek logon ko issi tarah badlay diya kertay hain
  37,122,Yaqeenan yeh dono humaray momin bandon mein say thay
  37,123,Be-shak ilyas (alh-e-salam) bhi payghumbaron mein say thay
  37,124,Jabkay unhon ney apni qom say farmaya kay tum Allah say dartay nahi ho
  37,125,Kiya tum ba’al (naami butt) ko pukartay ho? Aur sabb say behtar khaliq ko chor detay ho
  37,126,Allah jo tumhara aur tumharay aglay tamam baap dadon ka rab hai
  37,127,Lekin qom ney unhen jhutlaya pus woh zaroor (azab mein) hazir rakhay jayen gay
  37,128,Siwaye Allah Taalaa kay mukhlis bandon kay
  37,129,Hum ney (ilyas alh-e-salam) ka zikar-e-khair pichlon mein bhi baqi rakha
  37,130,Kay ilyas per salam ho
  37,131,Hum neki kerney walon ko issi tarah badla detay hain
  37,132,Be-shak woh humaray eman daar bandon mein say tha
  37,133,Be-shak loot (alh-e-salam bhi) payghumbaron mein say thay
  37,134,Hum ney unhen aur unn kay ghar walon sab ko nijat di
  37,135,Ba-juz uss burhiya kay jo peechay reh janey walon mein reh gaee
  37,136,Phir hum ney auron ko halak ker diya
  37,137,Aur tum to subha honey per unn ki bastiyon kay pass say guzartay ho
  37,138,Aur raat ko bhi kiya phir bhi nahi samajhtay
  37,139,Aur bila-shuba younus (alh-e-salam) nabiyon mein say thay
  37,140,Jab bhag ker phonchay bhari kashti per
  37,141,Phir qura-andazi hui to maghloob hogaye
  37,142,To phir unhen machli ney nigal liya aur woh khud apnay aap ko malamat kerney lag gaye
  37,143,Pus agar yeh paki biyan kerney walon mein say na hotay
  37,144,To logon kay uthaye janey kay din tak uss kay pet mein hi rehtay
  37,145,Pus unhen hum ney chatyal medan mein daal diya aur woh uss waqt beemar thay
  37,146,Aur unn per saya kerney wala aik bel daar darakht hum ney uga diya
  37,147,Aur hum ney unhen aik lakh bulkay aur ziyadah aadmiyon ki taraf bheja
  37,148,Pus woh eman laye aur hum ney unhen aik zamaney tak aish-o-ishrat di
  37,149,Inn say daryaft kijiye! Kay kiya aap kay rab ki to betiyan hain aur inn kay betay hain
  37,150,Ya yeh uss waqt mojood thay jabkay hum ney farishton ko moanniss peda kiya
  37,151,Aagah raho! Kay yeh log sirf apni iftra per-dazi say keh rahey hain
  37,152,Kay Allah Taalaa ki aulad hai. Yeqeenan yeh mehaz jhootay hain
  37,153,Kiya Allah Taalaa ney apnay liye betiyon ko beton per tarjeeh di
  37,154,Tumhen kiya hogaya hai kaisay hukum lagatay phirtay ho
  37,155,Kiya tum iss qadar bhi nahi samajhtay
  37,156,Ya tumharay pass iss ki koi saaf daleel hai
  37,157,To jao agar sachay ho to apni hi kitab ley aao
  37,158,Aur inn logon ney to Allah kay aur jinnaat kay darmiyan bhi qarabat daari theraee hai aur halankay khud jinnaat ko maloom hai kay woh (iss aqeeday kay log azab kay samney) paish kiyey jayen gay
  37,159,Jo kuch yeh (Allah kay baray mein) biyan ker rahey hain uss say Allah Taalaa bilkul pak hai
  37,160,Siwaye Allah kay mukhlis bandon kay
  37,161,Yaqeen mano kay tum sab aur tumharay maboodaan (baatil)
  37,162,Kissi aik ko bhi behka nahi saktay
  37,163,Ba-juz uss kay jo jahannumi hi hai
  37,164,(farishton ka qol hai kay) hum mein say to her aik ki jagah muqarrar hai
  37,165,Aur hum to (bandag-e-elahee mein) saff basta kharay hain
  37,166,Aur uss ki tasbeeh biyan ker rahey hain
  37,167,Kuffaar to kaha kertay thay
  37,168,Kay agar humaray samney aglay logon ka zikar hota
  37,169,To hum bhi Allah kay cheedah banday bann jatay
  37,170,Lekin phir iss quran kay sath kufur ker gaye pus abb un-qareeb jaan len gay
  37,171,Aur albata humara wada pehlay hi apnay rasoolon kay liye sadir ho chuka hai
  37,172,Kay yaqeenan woh hi madad kiyey jayen gay
  37,173,Aur humara hi lashkar ghalib (aur bartar) rahey ga
  37,174,Abb aap kuch dino tak inn say mun pher lijiyey
  37,175,Aur enhen dekhtay rahiyey aur yeh bhi aagay chal ker dekh len gay
  37,176,Kiya yeh humaray azab ki jaldi macha rahey hain
  37,177,Suno! Jab humara azab inn kay medan mein utar aaye ga uss waqt unn ki jin ko muta-nabbay ker diya gaya tha bari buri subha hogi
  37,178,Aap kuch waqt tak inn ka khayal chor dijiyey
  37,179,Aur dekhtay rahiyey yeh bhi abhi abhi dekh len gay
  37,180,Pak hai aap ka rab jo bot bari izzat wala hai her uss cheez say (jo mushrik) biyan kertay hain
  37,181,Payghumbaron per salam hai
  37,182,Aur sab tarah ki tareef Allah kay liye hai jo saray jahan ka rab hai
  38,1,Suaad! Iss naseehat walay quran ki qasam
  38,2,Bulkay kufaar ghooroor-o-mukhalifat mein paray huyey hain
  38,3,Hum ney iss say pehlay bhi boht si ummaton ko tabah ker dala unhon ney her chand cheek pukaar ki lekin woh waqt chutkaray ka na tha
  38,4,Aur kafiron ko iss baat per tajjub hua kay unhi mein say aik unhen daraney wala aagaya aur kehney lagay kay yeh to jadoogar aur jhoota hai
  38,5,Kiya iss ney itnay saray maboodon ka aik hi mabood ker diya waqaee yeh boht hi ajeeb baat hai
  38,6,Unn kay sardaar yeh kehtay huyey chalay kay chalo ji aur apnay maboodon per jamay raho yaqeenan iss baat mein to koi gharz hai
  38,7,Hum ney to yeh baat pichlay deen mein bhi nahi suni kuch nahi yeh to sirf gharant hai
  38,8,Kiya hum sab mein issi per kalam-e-elahee nazil kiya gaya hai?Dar-asal yeh log meri wahee ki taraf say shak mein hain bulkay (sahih yeh hai kay) enhon ney abb tak mera azab chakha hi nahi
  38,9,Ya kiya inn kay pass teray zabardast fayyaz rab ki rehmat kay khazaney hain
  38,10,Ya kiya aasman-o-zamin aur inn kay damiyan ki her cheez ki badshaat inn hi ki hai to phir yeh rasiyan taan ker charh jayen
  38,11,Yeh bhi (baray baray) lashkaron mein say shikast paya hua (chota sa) lashkar hai
  38,12,Inn say pehlay bhi qom-e-nooh aur aad aur meekhon walay firaon ney jhutlaya tha
  38,13,Aur samood ney aur qom-e-loot ney aur aeeka kay rehney walon ney bhi yehi (baray) lashkar thay
  38,14,Inn mein say aik bhi aisa na tha jiss ney rasoolon ki takzeeb na ki ho pus meri saza inn per sabit hogaee
  38,15,Enhen sirf aik cheekh ka intizar hai jiss mein koi tawaquff (aur dheel) nahi hai
  38,16,Aur unhon ney kaha aey humaray rab! Humari sir-nawisht tu humen roz-e-hisab say pehlay hi day dey
  38,17,Aap inn ki baton per sabar keren aur humaray banday dawood (alh-e-salam) ko yaad keren jo bari qooat wala tha yaqeenan woh boht rujoo kerney wala tha
  38,18,Hum ney paharon ko uss kay tabey ker rakha tha kay uss kay sath shaam ko aur subha tasbeeh khuwani keren
  38,19,Aur parindon ko bhi jama hoker sab kay sab uss kay zair-e-farman rehtay
  38,20,Aur hum ney uss ki saltanat ko mazboot ker diya tha aur ussay hikmat di thi aur baat ka faisla kerna
  38,21,Aur kiya tujhay jhagra kerney walon ki (bhi) khabar mili? Jab kay woh deewar phaand ker mehrab mein aagaye
  38,22,Jab yeh (hazrat) dawood (alh-e-salam) kay pass phonchay pus yeh unn say darr gaye unhon ney kaha khof na kijiyey! Hum do fareeq muqadma hain hum mein say aik ney ziyadti ki hai pus humaray darmiyan haq kay sath faisla ker dijiyey aur na-insafi na kijiyey aur humen seedhi raah bata dijiyey
  38,23,(suniyey) yeh mera bhai hai iss kay pass ninnanway dunbiyan hain aur meray pass aik hi dunbi hai lekin yeh mujh say keh raha hai kay apni yeh aik bhi mujh hi ko day dey aur mujh per baat mein bari sakhti baratta hai
  38,24,Aap ney farmaya! Iss ka apni dunbiyon kay sath teri aik dunbi mila lenay ka sawal be-shak teray upper aik zulm hai aur aksar hissay daar aur shareek (aisay hi hotay hain kay) aik doosray per zulm kertay hain siwaye unn kay jo eman laye aur jinhon ney nek amal kiyey aur aisay log boht hi kum hain aur (hazrat) dawwod (alh-e-salam) samajh gaye kay hum ney unhen aazmaya hai phir to apnay rab say istaghfaar kerney lagay aur aajzi kertay huyey gir paray aur (poori tarah) rujoo kiya
  38,25,Pus hum ney bhi unn ka woh (kasoor) maaf ker diya yaqeenan woh humaray nazdeek baray martabay walay aur boht achay thikaney walay hain
  38,26,Aey dawood! Hum ney tumhen zamin mein khalifa bana diya tum logon kay darmiyan haq kay sath faislay kero aur apni nafsani khuwaish ki perwi na kero werna woh tumhen Allah ki raah say bhatka deygi yaqeenan jo log Allah ki raah say bhatak jatay hain unn kay liye sakht azab hai iss liye kay unhon ney hisab kay din ko bhula diya hai
  38,27,Aur hum ney aasman-o-zamin aur inn kay darmiyan ki cheezon ko na-haq peda nahi kiya yeh guman to kafiron ka hai so kafiron kay liye kharabi hai aag ki
  38,28,Kiya hum unn logon ko jo eman laye aur nek amal kiye unn kay barabar ker den gay jo (humesha) zamin mein fasad machatay rahey ya perhezgaron ko badkaron jesa ker den gay
  38,29,Yeh ba-barkat kitab hai jissay hum ney aap ki taraf iss liye nazil farmaya hai kay log iss ki aayaton per ghor keren aur aqalmand iss say naseehat hasil keren
  38,30,Aur hum ney dawwod ko suleman (naami farzand) ata farmaya jo bara acha bandah tha aur beyhad rujoo kerney wala tha
  38,31,Jab unkay samney shaam kay waqt tez-ro khasay ghoray paish kiye gaye
  38,32,To kehney lagay mein ney apnay perwerdigar ki yaad per inn ghoron ki mohabbat ko tarjeeh di yahan tak kay (aftab) chup gaya
  38,33,Unn (ghoron) ko doobara meray samney lao! Phir to pindliyon aur gardano per hath pherna shoroo ker diya
  38,34,Aur hum ney suleman (alh-e-salam) ki aazmaeesh ki aur unn kay takhat per aik jism daal diya phir uss ney rujoo kiya
  38,35,Kaha kay aey meray rab! Mujhay bakhsh day aur mujhay aisa mulk ata farma jo meray siwa kissi (shaks) kay laeeq na ho tu bara hi denay wala hai
  38,36,Pus hum ney hawa ko unn kay ma-tehat ker diya woh aap kay hukum say jahan aap chahtay narmi say phoncha diya kerti thi
  38,37,Aur (taqatwar) jinnat ko bhi (unn ka ma-tehat ker diya) her imarat bananey walay ko aur ghota khor ko
  38,38,Aur doosray jinnat ko bhi jo zanjeeron mein jakray rehtay
  38,39,Yeh hai humara atiya abb tu ehsan ker ya rol rakh kuch hisab nahi
  38,40,Unn kay liye humaray pass bara taqarrub hai aur boht acha thikana hai
  38,41,Aur humaray banday ayub (alh-e-salam) ka (bhi) zikar ker jabkay uss ney apnay rab ko pukara kay mujhay shetan ney ranj aur dukh phonchaya hai
  38,42,Apna paaon maaro yeh nahaney ka thanda aur peenay ka paani hai
  38,43,Aur hum ney ussay uss ka poora kunba ata farmaya bulkay utna hi aur bhi issi kay sath apni (khaas) rehmat say aur aqalmandon ki naseehat kay liye
  38,44,Aur apnay hath mein tinko ka aik mutha (jhaaro) ley ker maar day aur qasam ka khilaf na ker sach to yeh hai kay hum ney ussay bara sabir banda paya woh bara nek banda tha aur bari hi raghbat rakhney wala
  38,45,"Humaray bandon ibarhim, ishaq aur yaqoob (al-e-heem-us-salam) ka bhi zikar kero jo hathon aur aankhon walay thay"
  38,46,Hum ney unhen aik khaas baat yani aakhirat ki yaad kay sath makhsoos ker diya tha
  38,47,Yeh sab humaray nazdeek bargazeedah aur behtareen log thay
  38,48,"Ismail, yasa aur zulkifil (al-e-heem-us-salam) ka bhi zikar ker dijiye. Yeh sab behtareen log thay"
  38,49,Yeh naseehat hai aur yaqeen mano kay perhezgaron ki bari achi jagah hai
  38,50,(yani hameshgi wali) jannaten jin kay darwazay unn kay liye khilay huyey hain
  38,51,Jin mein ba-faraghat takkiyey lagaye bethay huyey tarah tarah kay meway aur qisam qisam ki sharabon ki farmaeesh ker rahey hain
  38,52,Aur unn kay pass neechi nazron wali hum umar hooren hongi
  38,53,Yeh hai jiss ka wada tum say hisab kay din kay liye kiya jata tha
  38,54,Be-shak roziyan (khaas) humara atiya hain jin ka kabhi khatma hi nahi
  38,55,Yeh to hui jaza (yad rakho kay) sirkashon kay liye bari buri jagah hai
  38,56,Dozakh hai jiss mein woh jayen gay (aah) kiya hi bura bichona hai
  38,57,Yeh hai pus issay chakhen garum paani aur peep
  38,58,Iss kay ilawa aur tarah tarah kay azab
  38,59,Yeh aik qom hai jo tumharay sath (aag mein) janey wali hai koi khush aamdeed unn kay liye nahi hai yehi to jahannum mein janey walay hain
  38,60,Woh kahen gay bulkay tum hi ho jin kay liye koi khush amdeed nahi hai tum hi ney to issay pehlay hi say humaray samney laa rakha tha pus rehney ki bari buri jagah hai
  38,61,Woh kahen gay aey humaray rab! Jiss ney (kufur ki rasam) humaray liye pehlay say nikali ho uss kay haq mein jahannum ki dugni saza kerday
  38,62,Aur jahannumi kahen gay kiya baat hai kay woh log humen dikhaee nahi detay jinhen hum buray logon mein shumar kertay thay
  38,63,Kiya hum ney hi unn ka mazaq bana rakha tha ya humari nigahen unn say hat gaee hain
  38,64,Yaqeen jano kay dozakhiyon ka yeh jhagra zaroor hi hoga
  38,65,Keh dijiye! Kay mein to sirf khabaar kerney wala hun aur ba-juz Allah wahid ghalib kay aur koi laeeq ibadat nahi
  38,66,Jo perwerdigar hai aasmano ka aur zamin ka aur jo kuch inn kay darmiyan hai woh zabardast aur bara bakhsney wala hai
  38,67,Aap keh dijiye kay yeh boht bari khabar hai
  38,68,Jiss say tum be-parwah ho rahey ho
  38,69,Mujhay unn buland qadar farishton ki (baat cheet ka) koi ilm hi nahi jabkay woh takraar ker rahey thay
  38,70,Meri taraf faqat yehi wahee ki jati hai kay mein to saaf saaf aagah ker denay wala hun
  38,71,Jabkay aap kay rab ney farishton say irshad farmaya kay mein mitti say insan ko peda kerney wala hun
  38,72,So jab mein ussay theek thaak kerlon aur uss mein apni rooh phoonk don to tum sab uss kay samney sajjday mein gir parna
  38,73,Chunacha tamam farishton ney sajjdah kiya
  38,74,Magar iblees ney (na kiya) uss ney takabbur kiya aur woh tha kafiron mein say
  38,75,(Allah Taalaa ney) farmaya aey iblees! Tujhay issay sajjdah kerney say kiss cheez ney roka jissay mein ney apnay hathon say peda kiya kiya tu kuch ghamand mein aagaya hai? Ya tu baray darjay walon mein say hai
  38,76,Uss ney jawab diya mein iss say behtar hun tu ney mujhay aag say banaya aur iss mitti say banaya hai
  38,77,Irshad hua kay tu yahan say nikal ja tu mardood hua
  38,78,Aur tujh per qayamat kay din tak meri lanat-o-phitkaar hai
  38,79,Kehney laga meray rab mujhay logon kay uth kharay honey kay din tak mohlat day
  38,80,(Allah Taalaa ney) farmaya tu mohlat walon mein say hai
  38,81,Mutayyen waqt kay din tak
  38,82,Kehney laga phir to teri izzat ki qasam! Mein inn sab ko yaqeenan behka doon ga
  38,83,Ba-juz teray unn bandon kay jo cheedah aur pasndeedah hon
  38,84,Farmaya sach to yeh hai aur mein sach hi kaha kerta hun
  38,85,Kay tujh say aur teray tamam mannay walon say mein (bhi) jahannum ko bhar doon ga
  38,86,Keh dijiye! Kay mein tum say iss per koi badla talab nahi kerta aur na mein takaluf kerney walon mein say hun
  38,87,Yeh to tamam jahan walon kay liye sarasir naseehat (o-ibrat) hai
  38,88,Yaqeenan tum iss ki haqeeqat ko kuch hi waqt kay baad (sahih tor per) jaan logay
  39,1,Iss kitab ka utaarna Allah Taalaa ghalib ba-hikmat ki taraf say hai
  39,2,Yaqeenan hum ney iss kitab ko aap ki taraf haq kay sath nazil farmaya hai pus aap Allah hi ki ibadat keren ussi kay liye deen ko khalis kerti huyey
  39,3,Khabradaar! Allah Taalaa hi kay liye khalis ibadat kerna hai aur jin logon ney uss kay siwa auliya bana rakhay hain (aur kehtay hain) kay hum inn ki ibadat sirf iss liye kertay hain kay yeh (buzurg) Allah kay nazdeeki kay martabay tak humari rasaee kera den yeh log jiss baray mein ikhtilaf ker rahey hain iss ka (sacha) faisla Allah (khud) keray ga. Jhootay aur na-shukray (logon) ko Allah Taalaa raah nahi dikhata
  39,4,Agar Allah Taalaa ka iradah aulad hi ka hota to apni makhlooq mein say jissay chahata chun leta. (lekin) woh to pak hai wo wohi Allah Taalaa hai yagana aur qooat wala
  39,5,Nihayat achi tadbeer say uss ney aasmano aur zamin ko banaya woh raat ko din per aur din ko raat per lapet deta hai aur uss ney sooraj chaand ko kaam per laga rakha hai. Her aik muqarrara muddat tak chal raha hai yaqeen mano kay wohi zabardast aur gunahon ka bakhshney wala hai
  39,6,Uss ney tum sab ko aik hi jaan say peda kiya hai phir ussi say uss ka jora peda kiya aur tumharay liye chopayon mein say (aath nar-o-madah)utaray woh tumhen tumhari maaon kay peton mein aik banawat kay baad doosri banawat per banata hai teen teen andheron mein yehi Allah Taalaa tumhara rab hai ussi kay liye badshahaat hai uss kay siwa koi mabood nahi phir tum kahan behak rahey ho
  39,7,Agar tum na-shukri kero to (yaad rakho kay) Allah Taalaa tum (sab say) be-niyaz hai aur woh apnay bando ki na-shukri say khush nahi aur agar tum shukar kero to woh issay tumharay liye pasand keray ga aur koi kissi ka bojh nahi uthata phit tum sab ka lotna tumharay rab hi ki taraf hai. Tumhen woh batla dey ga jo tum kertay thay. Yaqeenan woh dilon tak ki baaton ka waqif hai
  39,8,Aur insan ko jab kabhi koi takleef phonchti hai to woh khoob rujoo hoker apnay rab ko pukarta hai phir jab Allah Taalaa ussay apnay pass say nemat ata farma deta hai to woh iss say pehlay jo dua kerta tha (ussay) bhool jata hai aur Allah Taalaa kay shareek muqarrar kerney lagta hai jiss say (auron ko bhi) uss ki raah say behkaye aap keh dijiye! Kay apnay kufur ka faeedah kuch din aur utha lo (aakhir) tu dozakhiyon mein honey wala hai
  39,9,Bhala jo shaks raaton kay auqaat sajjday aur qayaam ki halat mein (ibadat mein) guzaarta ho aakhirat say darta ho aur apnay rab ki rehmat ki umeed rakhta ho(aur jo iss kay bar-aks ho barbar ho saktay hain) batao to ilm walay aur be-ilm kiya barabar kay hain? Yaqeenan naseehat wohi hasil kertay hain jo aqalmand hon. (apnay rab ki taraf say)
  39,10,Kehdo kay aey meray eman walay bando! Apnay rab say dartay raho jo iss duniya mein neki kertay hain unn kay liye nek badla hai aur Allah Taalaa ki zamin boht kushadah hai sabar kerney walon hi ko unn ka poora poora be-shumaar ajar diya jata hai
  39,11,Aap keh dijiye! Kay mujhay hukum diya gaya hai kay Allah Taalaa ki iss tarah ibadat keroon kay ussi kay liye ibadat ko khalis ker loon
  39,12,Aur mujhay hukum diya gaya hai kay mein sab say pehla farmabardaar ban jaon
  39,13,Keh dijiyey! Kay mujhay to apnay rab ki na-farmani kertay huyey baray din kay azab ka khof aata lagta hai
  39,14,Keh dijiyey! Kay mein to khalis ker kay sirf apnay rab hi ki ibadat kerta hun
  39,15,Tum uss kay siwa jiss ki chahao ibadat kertay raho keh dijiyey! Kay haqeeqi ziyan kaar woh hain jo apnay aap ko aur apnay ehal ko qayamat kay din nuksan mein daal den gay yad rekho kay khullam khulla nuksan yehi hai
  39,16,Unehn neechay uper say aag kay (sholay misil)sayebaan (kay)dhaank rahey hongay. Yehi (azab) hai jin say Allah Taalaa apnay bando ko dara raha hai aey meray bando! Pus mujh say dartay raho
  39,17,Aur jin logon ney taghoot ki ibadat say perhez kiya aur (hama-tan) Allah Taalaa ki taraf mutawajja rahey woh khushkhabri kay mustahiq hain meray bando ko khushkhabri suna dijiyey
  39,18,Jo baat ko kaan laga ker suntay hain. Phir jo behtareen baat ho uss ki ittbaa kertay hain. Yehi hain jinhen Allah Taalaa ney hidayat ki hai aur yehi aqalmand bhi hain
  39,19,Bhala jiss shaks per azab ki baat saabit ho chuki hai to kiya aap ussay jo dozakh mein hai chura saktay hain
  39,20,Haan woh log jo apnay rab say dartay rahey unn kay liye bala khaney hain jinkay uper bhi banay banaye bala khaney hain (aur) unn kay neechay nehren beh rahi hain. Rab ka wada hai aur woh wada khilafi nahi kerta
  39,21,Kiya aap ney nahi dekha kay Allah Taalaa aasman say paani utaarta hai aur ussay zamin ki sooton mein phonchata hai phir issi kay zariyey mukhtalif qisam ki khetiyan ugata hai phit woh khushk hojati hain aur aap unhen zard rang dekhtay hain phir unhen reza reza ker deta hai iss mein aqalmando kay liye boht ziyadah naseehat hai
  39,22,Kiya woh shaks jiss ka seena Allah Taalaa ney islam kay liye khol diya hai pus woh apnay perwerdigar ki taraf say aik noor per hai aur halaki hai unn per jin kay dil yaad-e-elahi say (asar nahi letay bulkay) sakht hogaye hain. Yeh log sareeh gumrahi mein (mubtila) hain
  39,23,Allah Taalaa ney behtareen kalam nazil farmaya hai jo aisi kitab hai kay aapas mein milti julti aur baar baar dohraee hui aayaton ki hai jiss say unn logon kay rongtay kharay hojatay hain jo apnay rab ka khof rakhtay hain aakhir mein unn kay jisam aur dil Allah Taalaa kay zikar ki taraf naram hojatay hain yeh hai Allah Taalaa ki hidayat jiss kay zariyey jissay chahaye raah-e-raast per laga deta hai. Aur jissay Allah Taalaa hi raah bhula dey uss ka koi hadi nahi
  39,24,Bhala jo shaks qayamat kay din kay bad-tareen azab ki sapar (dhaal) apnay mun ko banaye ga. (aisay) zalimon say kaha jayega kay apnay kiyey ka (wabal) chakho
  39,25,Inn say pehlay walon ney bhi jhutlaya phir unn per wahan say azab aa para jahan say unn ko khayal bhi na tha
  39,26,Aur Allah Taalaa ney unhen zindagan-e-duniya mein ruswaee ka maza chakhaya aur abhi aakhirat ka to bara bhari azab hai kaash kay yeh log samajh len
  39,27,Aur yaqeenan hum ney iss quran mein logon kay liye her qisam ki misalen biyan ker di hain kiya ajab kay woh naseehat hasil kerlen
  39,28,Quran hai arabi mein jiss mein koi kuji nahi ho sakta hai kay woh perhezgari ikhtiyar ker len
  39,29,Allah Taalaa misal biyan farma raha hai aik woh shaks jiss mien boht say bahum zidd rakhney walay saajhi hain aur doosra woh shaks jo sirf aik hi ka (ghulam) hai kiya yeh dono sift mein yaksan hain Allah Taalaa hi kay liye sab tareef hai. Baat yeh hai kay inn mein say aksar log samajhtay nahi
  39,30,Yaqeenan khud aap ko bhi mot aayegi aur yeh sab bhi marney walay hain
  39,31,Phir tum sab kay sab qayamat kay din apnay rab kay samney jhagro gay